dct_title_s: Topographic map of the Island of Kauai, Kauai County, Hawaii
dct_description_sm: surveyed by the U.S. Geological Survey in cooperation with the Territory of Hawaii.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"R. B. Marshall, Chief Geographer"; "Topography by C. H. Birdseye, Geo. R. Davis...H. L. McDonald, T. H. Moncure, A. J. Ogle, O. G. Taylor, and W. H. Barringer"; surveyed in 1910.
Includes location map: The Hawaiian Islands.
